# 
Throw your team an amazing remote event.
Sit back while we do all the work.
Mini Exhibitions is a membership program for remote events. We create calendar events, send reminder emails, collect team members shipping addresses and ship them goodies — all so you don't have to.
Get the list of events
## Trusted by

# Unique and surprising events
We offer 100+ events ranging from mixology and cooking classes, art classes, magic shows, trivia… and events you didn’t even know you wanted like lockpicking, beekeeping, rock stacking, classical Pilates, and live-hosted spelling bees.
![](https://miniex-public.s3.us-west-1.amazonaws.com/manual-uploads/gifs/elephant-painting.webp)
We offer 100+ events ranging from mixology and cooking classes, art classes, magic shows, trivia… and events you didn’t even know you wanted like lockpicking, beekeeping, rock stacking, classical Pilates, and live-hosted spelling bees.
![](https://miniex-public.s3.us-west-1.amazonaws.com/manual-uploads/gifs/pumkin-hed.webp)
# Events for seasons and celebrating diversity
We have events for different holidays and diversity initiatives – so you can celebrate everyone at your company. And if you have a particular theme in mind, we’re always happy to customize an event for you, too.
![](https://miniex-public.s3.us-west-1.amazonaws.com/manual-uploads/gifs/pumkin-hed.webp)
We have events for different holidays and diversity initiatives – so you can celebrate everyone at your company. And if you have a particular theme in mind, we’re always happy to customize an event for you, too.
# Flat pricing no matter how many people show up
We’ll quote you a flat price per event. You don’t have to worry about whether too many or too few people show up – you know your price ahead of time. With us, you won’t have to waste time on your end going back and forth over budget and headcount.
![](https://miniex-public.s3.us-west-1.amazonaws.com/manual-uploads/gifs/simpsons-auditorium.webp)
We’ll quote you a flat price per event. You don’t have to worry about whether too many or too few people show up – you know your price ahead of time. With us, you won’t have to waste time on your end going back and forth over budget and headcount.
![](https://miniex-public.s3.us-west-1.amazonaws.com/manual-uploads/gifs/dog-at-computer.webp)
# We do the administrative work for you
We’ll create calendar events, we’ll send reminder emails. We’ll coordinate with your team to find a time that works. You can always choose to do these things on your end, but we’re ready to roll our sleeves up and do as much of the work as you’re comfortable to pass on to us.
![](https://miniex-public.s3.us-west-1.amazonaws.com/manual-uploads/gifs/dog-at-computer.webp)
We’ll create calendar events, we’ll send reminder emails. We’ll coordinate with your team to find a time that works. You can always choose to do these things on your end, but we’re ready to roll our sleeves up and do as much of the work as you’re comfortable to pass on to us.
# We love global teams
If your team is spread across the world, it’s no sweat for us. We work with lots of global teams – we’ll find times that work for everyone, handle shipping, and offer events that are perfect for international teams.
![](https://miniex-public.s3.us-west-1.amazonaws.com/manual-uploads/gifs/planet-emoji.webp)
If your team is spread across the world, it’s no sweat for us. We work with lots of global teams – we’ll find times that work for everyone, handle shipping, and offer events that are perfect for international teams.
![](https://miniex-public.s3.us-west-1.amazonaws.com/manual-uploads/gifs/aol.gif)
# Shared slack channels
We love shared Slack channels for running polls, sharing photos, answering questions, pre-event reminders, and hyping up our next event. And if you need to speak with someone on our team, we’re just a Slack message away.
![](https://miniex-public.s3.us-west-1.amazonaws.com/manual-uploads/gifs/aol.gif)
We love shared Slack channels for running polls, sharing photos, answering questions, pre-event reminders, and hyping up our next event. And if you need to speak with someone on our team, we’re just a Slack message away.

generated_description:
Mini Exhibitions is redefining how remote teams come together through engaging virtual events. Founded in New York and proudly part of Y Combinator's Batch W20, this startup is a small but capable team of two, offering a unique membership program that takes the hassle out of organizing remote activities. 

The mission is clear: to create memorable experiences for teams scattered across the globe. Whether it's a mixology class or a live spelling bee, Mini Exhibitions boasts a diverse catalog of over 100 quirky events that you'll love but might not have considered. They handle all the details—sending emails, managing RSVPs, and even shipping goodies to participants—allowing you to kick back and enjoy the fun without the administrative headache.

With flat pricing regardless of attendance, businesses won’t have to fret over budgeting for the number of participants. Plus, they cater to different cultural celebrations and can customize events as needed, reflecting a commitment to inclusivity within the workplace. 

They're not just about events either; Mini Exhibitions embraces technology to facilitate communication through shared Slack channels, making it easy to gauge interest and build excitement within your team.

Trusted by notable companies like Amazon, Spotify, and Stripe, Mini Exhibitions is rapidly establishing itself in the marketplace of remote team engagement. So, if you’re looking to enliven your team's virtual experience without lifting a finger, head on over to [Mini Exhibitions](https://miniexhibitions.com/) and let them do the heavy lifting for you.
